The strong scent of spring flowers in full bloom fills the air. An old tower, marking southernmost place of Jarvonia, stands atop the looming cliffs. Looking out across the ocean, one can see the silhouette of Wallisia in the distance.

Winter's End is a location that can be found in the Jarvonia region.

Faction

Winter's End is a member of the following factions:

Jarvonia

Activities

The following activities always available at this location.

Sea fishing (Cage)
Spring cave foraging

Hidden Activity

These Hidden Activities are only visible if you meet the requirements first.

Spring bat tracking

Service

The following services can be used at this location.

Ruined Trinketry Bench (Basic)
